               <p>Q. Have you lost any thing?</p>
               <p>Miller. My wife knows, I don't know what I lost.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="174805260020"></xptr>Q. Is the Prisoner your servant?</p>
               <p>Miller. I don't know any thing of him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17480526-23-person254">
                  Mary 
                  Miller 
               <interp inst="t17480526-23-person254" type="surname" value="Miller"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17480526-23-person254" type="given" value="Mary"></interp>
